      <title>为什么苏格兰的政治危机可能塑造英国的未来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/why-snp-s-struggles-in-scotland-could-shape-politics-across-the-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏格兰民族党陷入混乱——多年来是英国最有效和最具统治力的政党之一——在几个月后的英国大选之前，这可能会产生深远的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/why-snp-s-struggles-in-scotland-could-shape-politics-across-the-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 14:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使有肯·格里芬的支持，参议院共和党人仍在金钱竞赛中失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/even-with-ken-griffin-s-support-senate-republicans-are-losing-the-money-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院共和党人将亿万富翁肯·格里芬、雪佛龙公司和西方石油公司视为最大捐助者，但筹集资金最多的是众议院的民主党人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/even-with-ken-griffin-s-support-senate-republicans-are-losing-the-money-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 14:45:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国禁令解除后，RedBird IMI 将开始出售 Telegraph</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/redbird-imi-to-kick-off-sale-of-telegraph-after-uk-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，RedBird IMI 将放弃对《电讯报》的收购，此举可能会引发英国报业集团的另一场竞购战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/redbird-imi-to-kick-off-sale-of-telegraph-after-uk-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 14:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯与伊朗军事联盟引起以色列担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/russia-iran-military-alliance-gives-israel-cause-for-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月以色列与伊朗的导弹袭击可能会暂停，但这两个宿敌之间前所未有的直接冲突引发了人们对俄罗斯在中东危机中所扮演角色的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/russia-iran-military-alliance-gives-israel-cause-for-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 14:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新的加沙人质视频增加了内塔尼亚胡对拉法的热度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/gaza-hostage-video-complicates-netanyahu-decision-on-rafah-offensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一段显示一名被关押在加沙的美国-以色列俘虏的视频将公众的注意力集中到了 130 多名人质的命运上，这使得总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡决定何时对哈马斯在拉法的最后据点发起进攻的决定变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/gaza-hostage-video-complicates-netanyahu-decision-on-rafah-offensive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 13:19:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非资产飙升，稳定联盟的可能性不断增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/rand-traders-cheer-as-anc-s-support-dips-further-in-latest-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市触及一月份以来的最高水平，欧元债券上涨，兰特涨幅创今年以来最高水平，此前一项民意调查的公布增加了下个月全国选举中出现亲市场联盟的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/rand-traders-cheer-as-anc-s-support-dips-further-in-latest-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 12:47:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非非国大支持率在投票前下滑； EFF支持率暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/south-africa-s-anc-support-slips-before-vote-eff-backing-slumps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，在下个月的选举之前，选民对南非执政党非洲人国民大会的支持率进一步下滑，左翼经济自由斗士将选票泄露给了前总统雅各布·祖马支持的新政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/south-africa-s-anc-support-slips-before-vote-eff-backing-slumps</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 11:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将在 2025 年额外承担 80 亿欧元的净债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/germany-to-take-on-additional-8-billion-in-net-new-debt-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国联邦政府明年将拥有更多借贷余地，新债务净额将约为 240 亿欧元（合 258 亿美元），而不是财政部 7 月份预测的 160 亿欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/germany-to-take-on-additional-8-billion-in-net-new-debt-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 11:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟以新的数字规则打击快时尚巨头 Shein</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/eu-hits-fast-fashion-giant-shein-with-new-digital-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[快时尚公司 Shein 已被纳入欧盟旗舰规则的范围内，该规则旨在打击在线非法和有害内容，旨在阻止假冒商品在该平台上的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/eu-hits-fast-fashion-giant-shein-with-new-digital-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 10:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
